{"id":3433,"date":"2026-03-05T10:28:20","date_gmt":"2026-03-05T10:28:20","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/?p=3433"},"modified":"2026-03-06T13:43:35","modified_gmt":"2026-03-06T13:43:35","slug":"zakaj-so-plasticni-selitveni-zaboji-pametnejsa-izbira-od-kartona","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/zakaj-so-plasticni-selitveni-zaboji-pametnejsa-izbira-od-kartona\/","title":{"rendered":"Why Renting Plastic Moving Crates is Smarter Than Buying Cardboard Boxes?"},"content":{"rendered":"<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"3433\" class=\"elementor elementor-3433\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8ea0773 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8ea0773\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca798d7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"ca798d7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"225\" height=\"300\" src=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-225x300.png\" class=\"attachment-medium size-medium wp-image-2244\" alt=\"Plasti\u010dni selitveni zaboji Rabimbox za varno selitev\" srcset=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-225x300.png 225w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-768x1025.png 768w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-1151x1536.png 1151w, https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/08\/Untitled-design-1535x2048.png 1535w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 225px) 100vw, 225px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fbb1d30 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fbb1d30\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4e8a853 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"4e8a853\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\"><a href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">Why Renting Plastic Moving Crates is Smarter Than Buying Cardboard?<\/a><\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2f07956 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2f07956\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e4037c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"3e4037c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-path-to-node=\"6\">Every move starts with the same question: <i data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"44\">\"Where can I find strong enough boxes?\"<\/i> Traditional <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"91\">moving packaging<\/b> in the form of cardboard often lets us down, as the bottom tends to give way under heavier loads, and it offers no protection against moisture or dirt. At Rabimbox, we solve this problem with <b data-path-to-node=\"6\" data-index-in-node=\"281\">the rental of professional crates<\/b>, which are your best investment for a safe move of your valuables without unnecessary stress.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"7\"><b data-path-to-node=\"7\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Main benefits of renting Rabimbox crates:<\/b><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"8\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Superior protection for your belongings:<\/b> Durable plastic protects your items from moisture, dust, and impacts that would be fatal for cardboard.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Speed and ease without packing tape:<\/b> Forget hours of taping and assembling boxes\u2014our crates are ready instantly; just load them and snap the lid shut.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Maximum hygiene and cleanliness:<\/b> Every crate is thoroughly cleaned and sanitized after use, ensuring perfect hygiene for every new customer.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"8,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">No waste accumulation:<\/b> No need to dispose of boxes at a landfill after the move; we take them away, while you enjoy your clean new home.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-path-to-node=\"9\"><strong>How to safely pack fragile items? (A solution for a stress-free transport)<\/strong><\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"10\">The greatest stress during a move is caused by the fear that valuable contents\u2014such as glasses, electronics, or artwork\u2014might be damaged during transport. Our <b data-path-to-node=\"10\" data-index-in-node=\"141\">moving packaging<\/b> with its hard shell completely eliminates this problem, as it does not buckle under the weight of other crates.<\/p><p data-path-to-node=\"11\"><b data-path-to-node=\"11\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Here is the recipe for safe packing:<\/b><\/p><ul data-path-to-node=\"12\"><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,0,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Layered stacking:<\/b> Place a softer layer at the bottom of the crate, then heavier items, and the lightest and most fragile pieces on top.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,1,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">No empty space:<\/b> Fill the gaps with paper or textiles to prevent the contents from moving during the drive.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,2,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Safe vertical stacking:<\/b> Unlike cardboard, our crates can be stacked high on top of each other, as they are designed for stable stacking without the risk of collapsing.<\/p><\/li><li><p data-path-to-node=\"12,3,0\"><b data-path-to-node=\"12,3,0\" data-index-in-node=\"0\">Clear labeling:<\/b> Each crate has a dedicated space for a label where you can write the contents (e.g., \u201cKitchen \u2013 Fragile\u201d), which will save you hours of time during unpacking.<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-path-to-node=\"13\">By renting the right crates and using professional techniques, your move will be fast, safe, and ecologically responsible.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-71ab425 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"71ab425\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-821ef00 elementor-button-info elementor-align-center elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"821ef00\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-button-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"https:\/\/rabimbox.si\/en\/izposoja\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Order moving crates<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t